    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the chassis has received proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity. The suspension remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this platform is renowned for. A mechanically honest machine ready for the apex.",
