    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a well-maintained, reliable car that has been cared for with an eye for longevity. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though under close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper consistent with careful daily use. The alloy wheels are in excellent shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a premium space; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster and no tears or thinning. All electronics, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, function exactly as they did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule, with a recent oil service and brake pad replacement performed just 1,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly across the rev range, and the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. While not a concours trailer queen, it is a high-quality, honest example that drives beautifully and looks sharp in any driveway. Included are two keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a folder of recent service records.",
